      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions documented and traceable; boundary conditions replicated in simulation within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions (flow rate 2.5 L/min, rotational speed 2500 RPM) replicated in CFD boundary conditions. Inlet velocity profile derived from PIV measurements. Fluid properties matched to phosphate-buffered saline at 37°C as specified in experimental protocol."
