      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published comparative studies for internal rotating flows at similar Reynolds numbers. Non-Newtonian blood rheology modeled using Carreau-Yasuda model with published constants for human blood. Model form choices documented in simulation plan."
