    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out or not assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for Class II devices at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions are validated against FDA benchmark data with acceptable quantitative agreement. The overall evidence package supports acceptance of the model for the stated COU.",
